{"4103150": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "捉鬼敢生隊", "steam_appid": 4103150, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【遊戲概述】</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你是一個期待在校園裡歌頌青春的普通大學新生，卻忽然每晚都在夢中受到神秘女鬼的桃色襲擊！性癖逐漸被扭曲、倍受困擾的你到神社求助，竟被告知需要到城市各處降服四大惡鬼才能解開詛咒……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >潛入各個鬧鬼地點後，你發現傳聞中的惡靈竟然都是充滿魅力的女鬼！？作為地縛靈的她們正因各自的執念而飽受折磨、甚至失去理智，一切的背後似乎還有不為人知的秘密......？請發揮你的智慧與陽氣，能拯救大家的只有你！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【遊戲特色】</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4103150/extras/007a1ee188daa2a747c3b67a9015b629.avif?t=1776198341\" width=1560 height=916 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4103150/extras/94ac944c8214490365ab73602e54a1a7.poster.avif?t=1776198341\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4103150/extras/94ac944c8214490365ab73602e54a1a7.webm?t=1776198341\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4103150/extras/94ac944c8214490365ab73602e54a1a7.mp4?t=1776198341\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4103150/extras/56a48a5ee45ba182559d20471454cedb.poster.avif?t=1776198341\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4103150/extras/56a48a5ee45ba182559d20471454cedb.webm?t=1776198341\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4103150/extras/56a48a5ee45ba182559d20471454cedb.mp4?t=1776198341\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>✦精細的全動態H場景演出</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>✦27段H劇情</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>✦含差分多達350張以上的CG</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>✦差分豐富的動態H模式</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>✦輕鬆簡單的解謎探索及橫向塔防玩法</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>✦女主角全語音演出</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>✦女主角全動態立繪</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>✦逾150,000字文本</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【遊戲系統】</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4103150/extras/3dd1db9687fc5ac9daf807d539df5d9d.avif?t=1776198341\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4103150/extras/6858d2da815b8ec452b40c222bb25aac.avif?t=1776198341\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>—地圖探索解謎—</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家需要在各個鬧鬼地點進行探索，搜集女鬼出沒的時程、行為習慣、甚至弱點與秘密。關鍵資料都會自動記錄在捉鬼手冊裡，請利用這些線索完成解謎，突破女鬼們的心防並把握機會注入陽氣❤！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索時還請小心，慎重作出每個選擇、遵守每個鬧鬼地點的規矩。一旦理智值清零，反而會面臨來自女鬼的襲擊……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4103150/extras/a3fa12942391a832a7b9bbd81b586ce6.avif?t=1776198341\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>—輕鬆簡單的橫向塔防—</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >若進入鬼氣最盛的「惡域時段」，你將會迎來女鬼與其他遊魂野鬼的襲擊！除了善用道具抵禦攻擊，還可以用你的精液召喚各種式神。編排出最強的式神隊伍，把遊魂野鬼通通捕獲、轉化成行動資金吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >只要在塔防中撐過特定時間，鬼氣消散後她們也會離開！不過如果能戰勝女鬼，你就可以盡情享受臉紅心跳的陽氣注入時間❤ 每次戰勝女鬼，下次塔防的難度就會更高，但可能會解鎖更多色色的互動？......</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【人物介紹】</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4103150/extras/9a7c040c3f0f62c243a5d96abc377ce9.poster.avif?t=1776198341\" width=616 height=422 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4103150/extras/9a7c040c3f0f62c243a5d96abc377ce9.webm?t=1776198341\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4103150/extras/9a7c040c3f0f62c243a5d96abc377ce9.mp4?t=1776198341\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>名稱：幽子</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >住處：老舊日式公寓的四樓邊間</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >被稱作「四樓公寓的白衣惡鬼」，實際上是陰沉內向的幽靈。不善言辭，十分膽小、意外容易被嚇到，心靈受傷時會躲起來。情感產生波動時，即使她努力不表現出來，身邊的鬼火還是會暴露她的想法。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >討厭與人類接觸，對三次元人類極度不信任。然而這樣的她，有著不為人知的秘密愛好……？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4103150/extras/a646698d26ff5d3963586785bb546a74.poster.avif?t=1776198341\" width=616 height=422 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4103150/extras/a646698d26ff5d3963586785bb546a74.webm?t=1776198341\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4103150/extras/a646698d26ff5d3963586785bb546a74.mp4?t=1776198341\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>名稱：卡蜜拉·馮·德古拉</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >住處：偏遠郊區的廢棄酒店</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >人稱「灼眼的吸血鬼教祖」，自稱瞧不起身為「平凡人類」的男主角，自從男主角出現後便一直嘗試對他做各種惡作劇。與崇拜她、渴求永生的信徒們盤踞在廢棄酒店裡，奇怪和危險的作風使他們被視為邪教。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在信徒眼中看似無所不能的她，內心卻隱藏著一個不可告人的秘密……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4103150/extras/c41f9b882018e53f9e12787c07775a57.poster.avif?t=1776198341\" width=616 height=422 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4103150/extras/c41f9b882018e53f9e12787c07775a57.webm?t=1776198341\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4103150/extras/c41f9b882018e53f9e12787c07775a57.mp4?t=1776198341\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>名稱：粽粽</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >住處：以靈異勝地而聞名的公園</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以「冰冷的公園邪靈」之名被大眾所恐懼、是本地最知名的都市傳說。真身是呆滯無口的笨蛋殭屍娘，非常笨拙，不知為何總是身穿著羞恥的服裝在公園內四處蹦跳。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >無法正常理解人類的觀念和行為，經常做出各種把路人嚇得魂飛魄散的舉動，然而她之所以做盡怪事，都是源自從很久很久以前就有的唯一一個願望……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4103150/extras/03424e09a44efb2fdb284a4121a9ff99.poster.avif?t=1776198341\" width=616 height=422 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4103150/extras/03424e09a44efb2fdb284a4121a9ff99.webm?t=1776198341\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4103150/extras/03424e09a44efb2fdb284a4121a9ff99.mp4?t=1776198341\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>名稱：哈塞普蘇</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >住處：突然關閉的大型博物館</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >神秘得讓人難以捉摸、聰明且強大的遠古女王，突然從棺木中甦醒。古代文獻稱她為「滅世的美麗」，舉手投足都充滿魅力。與之相反，與她一同甦醒的丈夫性格卻懦弱膽小、胸無大志。當她看著丈夫與身邊一切時，眼神總是別有深意。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >無論是囚禁博物館的保安，還是在博物館內培養亡靈大軍準備攻打全世界，她所做的一切都出於某個原因……</p>", "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【遊戲概述】</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你是一個期待在校園裡歌頌青春的普通大學新生，卻忽然每晚都在夢中受到神秘女鬼的桃色襲擊！性癖逐漸被扭曲、倍受困擾的你到神社求助，竟被告知需要到城市各處降服四大惡鬼才能解開詛咒……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >潛入各個鬧鬼地點後，你發現傳聞中的惡靈竟然都是充滿魅力的女鬼！？作為地縛靈的她們正因各自的執念而飽受折磨、甚至失去理智，一切的背後似乎還有不為人知的秘密......？請發揮你的智慧與陽氣，能拯救大家的只有你！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【遊戲特色】</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4103150/extras/007a1ee188daa2a747c3b67a9015b629.avif?t=1776198341\" width=1560 height=916 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4103150/extras/94ac944c8214490365ab73602e54a1a7.poster.avif?t=1776198341\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4103150/extras/94ac944c8214490365ab73602e54a1a7.webm?t=1776198341\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4103150/extras/94ac944c8214490365ab73602e54a1a7.mp4?t=1776198341\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4103150/extras/56a48a5ee45ba182559d20471454cedb.poster.avif?t=1776198341\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4103150/extras/56a48a5ee45ba182559d20471454cedb.webm?t=1776198341\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4103150/extras/56a48a5ee45ba182559d20471454cedb.mp4?t=1776198341\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>✦精細的全動態H場景演出</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>✦27段H劇情</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>✦含差分多達350張以上的CG</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>✦差分豐富的動態H模式</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>✦輕鬆簡單的解謎探索及橫向塔防玩法</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>✦女主角全語音演出</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>✦女主角全動態立繪</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>✦逾150,000字文本</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【遊戲系統】</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4103150/extras/3dd1db9687fc5ac9daf807d539df5d9d.avif?t=1776198341\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4103150/extras/6858d2da815b8ec452b40c222bb25aac.avif?t=1776198341\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>—地圖探索解謎—</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家需要在各個鬧鬼地點進行探索，搜集女鬼出沒的時程、行為習慣、甚至弱點與秘密。關鍵資料都會自動記錄在捉鬼手冊裡，請利用這些線索完成解謎，突破女鬼們的心防並把握機會注入陽氣❤！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索時還請小心，慎重作出每個選擇、遵守每個鬧鬼地點的規矩。一旦理智值清零，反而會面臨來自女鬼的襲擊……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4103150/extras/a3fa12942391a832a7b9bbd81b586ce6.avif?t=1776198341\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>—輕鬆簡單的橫向塔防—</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >若進入鬼氣最盛的「惡域時段」，你將會迎來女鬼與其他遊魂野鬼的襲擊！除了善用道具抵禦攻擊，還可以用你的精液召喚各種式神。編排出最強的式神隊伍，把遊魂野鬼通通捕獲、轉化成行動資金吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >只要在塔防中撐過特定時間，鬼氣消散後她們也會離開！不過如果能戰勝女鬼，你就可以盡情享受臉紅心跳的陽氣注入時間❤ 每次戰勝女鬼，下次塔防的難度就會更高，但可能會解鎖更多色色的互動？......</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【人物介紹】</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4103150/extras/9a7c040c3f0f62c243a5d96abc377ce9.poster.avif?t=1776198341\" width=616 height=422 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4103150/extras/9a7c040c3f0f62c243a5d96abc377ce9.webm?t=1776198341\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4103150/extras/9a7c040c3f0f62c243a5d96abc377ce9.mp4?t=1776198341\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>名稱：幽子</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >住處：老舊日式公寓的四樓邊間</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >被稱作「四樓公寓的白衣惡鬼」，實際上是陰沉內向的幽靈。不善言辭，十分膽小、意外容易被嚇到，心靈受傷時會躲起來。情感產生波動時，即使她努力不表現出來，身邊的鬼火還是會暴露她的想法。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >討厭與人類接觸，對三次元人類極度不信任。然而這樣的她，有著不為人知的秘密愛好……？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4103150/extras/a646698d26ff5d3963586785bb546a74.poster.avif?t=1776198341\" width=616 height=422 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4103150/extras/a646698d26ff5d3963586785bb546a74.webm?t=1776198341\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4103150/extras/a646698d26ff5d3963586785bb546a74.mp4?t=1776198341\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>名稱：卡蜜拉·馮·德古拉</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >住處：偏遠郊區的廢棄酒店</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >人稱「灼眼的吸血鬼教祖」，自稱瞧不起身為「平凡人類」的男主角，自從男主角出現後便一直嘗試對他做各種惡作劇。與崇拜她、渴求永生的信徒們盤踞在廢棄酒店裡，奇怪和危險的作風使他們被視為邪教。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在信徒眼中看似無所不能的她，內心卻隱藏著一個不可告人的秘密……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4103150/extras/c41f9b882018e53f9e12787c07775a57.poster.avif?t=1776198341\" width=616 height=422 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4103150/extras/c41f9b882018e53f9e12787c07775a57.webm?t=1776198341\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4103150/extras/c41f9b882018e53f9e12787c07775a57.mp4?t=1776198341\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>名稱：粽粽</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >住處：以靈異勝地而聞名的公園</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以「冰冷的公園邪靈」之名被大眾所恐懼、是本地最知名的都市傳說。真身是呆滯無口的笨蛋殭屍娘，非常笨拙，不知為何總是身穿著羞恥的服裝在公園內四處蹦跳。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >無法正常理解人類的觀念和行為，經常做出各種把路人嚇得魂飛魄散的舉動，然而她之所以做盡怪事，都是源自從很久很久以前就有的唯一一個願望……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4103150/extras/03424e09a44efb2fdb284a4121a9ff99.poster.avif?t=1776198341\" width=616 height=422 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4103150/extras/03424e09a44efb2fdb284a4121a9ff99.webm?t=1776198341\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4103150/extras/03424e09a44efb2fdb284a4121a9ff99.mp4?t=1776198341\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>名稱：哈塞普蘇</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >住處：突然關閉的大型博物館</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >神秘得讓人難以捉摸、聰明且強大的遠古女王，突然從棺木中甦醒。古代文獻稱她為「滅世的美麗」，舉手投足都充滿魅力。與之相反，與她一同甦醒的丈夫性格卻懦弱膽小、胸無大志。當她看著丈夫與身邊一切時，眼神總是別有深意。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >無論是囚禁博物館的保安，還是在博物館內培養亡靈大軍準備攻打全世界，她所做的一切都出於某個原因……</p>", "short_description": "為了解開身上的詛咒，你被迫接下委託，直面史上最兇惡最恐怖的四位女鬼！但你發現她們好像跟傳聞中不太一樣......？ 在小心防備各種致命襲擊的同時，透過每晚的探索與互動，找出降服她們、壓制鬼氣的方法吧。 一切的關鍵，就在你的下半身♂！", "supported_languages": "繁體中文<strong>*</strong>, 英文, 日文<strong>*</strong>, 簡體中文<strong>*</strong>, 韓文<br><strong>*</strong>具備完整音效支援的語言", "header_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4103150/564abaccb2fe0a3838437ad96ad7de6cc6e89add/header_tchinese.jpg?t=1776198341", "capsule_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4103150/d619d45413dc6e5ba552368565a058ef9e383e24/capsule_231x87_tchinese.jpg?t=1776198341", "capsule_imagev5": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4103150/d619d45413dc6e5ba552368565a058ef9e383e24/capsule_184x69_tchinese.jpg?t=1776198341", "website": null, "pc_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>最低配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>作業系統 *:</strong> Windows7/8/10/11<br></li><li><strong>處理器:</strong> Intel Core i3<br></li><li><strong>記憶體:</strong> 4 GB 記憶體<br></li><li><strong>顯示卡:</strong> NVIDIA GeForce GTX 560 / AMD Radeon HD 6870  DirectX 版本: 11<br></li><li><strong>儲存空間:</strong> 2.98 GB 可用空間<br></li><li><strong>音效卡:</strong> DirectSound</li></ul>", "recommended": "<strong>建議配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>作業系統 *:</strong> Windows7/8/10/11<br></li><li><strong>處理器:</strong> Intel Core i3<br></li><li><strong>記憶體:</strong> 8 GB 記憶體<br></li><li><strong>顯示卡:</strong> NVIDIA GeForce GTX 760 / AMD Radeon HD 6870  DirectX 版本: 11<br></li><li><strong>儲存空間:</strong> 3 GB 可用空間<br></li><li><strong>音效卡:</strong> DirectSound</li></ul>"}, "mac_requirements": [], "linux_requirements": [